based electric field estimate, which\ncorrects the poor inductivity of the raw DAVE4VM estimate. This method is less\nsensitive to the changes of cadence, but still faces significant issues for the\nlowest of considered cadences ($\\geq$2 hours). We find several potential\nproblems in both PDFI- and DAVE4VM-based injection estimates and conclude that\nthe quality of both should be surveyed further in controlled environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Jun 2019 11:18:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-02"}
